message.text:
#IABFAdvisory
 
Re: E-Book Access for First Semester S.Y. 2025-2026

Attention, IABF!

For those utilizing E-Books as part of your course requirements, please take note of the following important reminders:
 
This semester, Digital Solutions (DS) access codes are obtained by signing the Student Undertaking form, with fees charged directly to your student account.

The corresponding amount appears in the Statement of Account within 1–2 months after receiving the access codes (Cengage and Pearson) or after account activation (McGraw-Hill).

Access codes are released daily, subject to stock availability. Requests submitted after 6:00 PM are processed the next business day.
 
Kindly scan the QR code or check the following links below:
 
CENGAGE
⁦https://bit.ly/CengageSU⁩
 
PEARSON
⁦https://bit.ly/PearsonSU⁩
 
MCGRAW-HILL
https://bit.ly/McgrawhillSU⁩  
 
Thank you for your cooperation.
 
Souce: Business Administration Department
 
#SoaringGreaterHeights
 
Pubmat by Yesha Eugenio and Alyanna Madrideo

message.text:
#IABFAdvisory
 
Re: E-Book Access for First Semester S.Y. 2025-2026

Attention, IABF!

For those utilizing E-Books as part of your course requirements, please take note of the following important reminders:
 
This semester, Digital Solutions (DS) access codes are obtained by signing the Student Undertaking form, with fees charged directly to your student account.

The corresponding amount appears in the Statement of Account within 1–2 months after receiving the access codes (Cengage and Pearson) or after account activation (McGraw-Hill).

Access codes are released daily, subject to stock availability. Requests submitted after 6:00 PM are processed the next business day.
 
Kindly scan the QR code or check the following links below:
 
CENGAGE
⁦https://bit.ly/CengageSU⁩
 
PEARSON
⁦https://bit.ly/PearsonSU⁩
 
MCGRAW-HILL
https://bit.ly/McgrawhillSU⁩  
 
Thank you for your cooperation.
 
Souce: Business Administration Department
 
#SoaringGreaterHeights
 
Pubmat by Yesha Eugenio and Alyanna Madrideo

message.text:
#IABFAdvisory
 
Re: E-Book Access for First Semester S.Y. 2025-2026

Attention, IABF!

For those utilizing E-Books as part of your course requirements, please take note of the following important reminders:
 
This semester, Digital Solutions (DS) access codes are obtained by signing the Student Undertaking form, with fees charged directly to your student account.

The corresponding amount appears in the Statement of Account within 1–2 months after receiving the access codes (Cengage and Pearson) or after account activation (McGraw-Hill).

Access codes are released daily, subject to stock availability. Requests submitted after 6:00 PM are processed the next business day.
 
Kindly scan the QR code or check the following links below:
 
CENGAGE
⁦https://bit.ly/CengageSU⁩
 
PEARSON
⁦https://bit.ly/PearsonSU⁩
 
MCGRAW-HILL
https://bit.ly/McgrawhillSU⁩  
 
Thank you for your cooperation.
 
Souce: Business Administration Department
 
#SoaringGreaterHeights
 
Pubmat by Yesha Eugenio and Alyanna Madrideo

message.text:
𝐘𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐬 𝐌𝐚𝐝𝐞 𝐈𝐭 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐥-𝐍𝐨𝐰 𝐋𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐊𝐞𝐞𝐩 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜 𝐆𝐨𝐢𝐧𝐠!

Thank you, ITHM Tams, for stopping by, sharing your smiles, and becoming part of our story at the ITHM Student Council booth! 

Every photo, every laugh, every moment spent with you was a reminder of what this council stands for—community, leadership, and joy.

We’re just getting started, and there’s more in store for you in the coming days. So stay tuned, keep that smile on, and let’s continue creating the heartbeat of the ITHM community.

Photos by: Ashley Sunggayan, Enzo Abello

Thank you, ITHM Tams, for stopping by, sharing your smiles, and becoming part of our story at the ITHM Student Council booth! 

Every photo, every laugh, every moment spent with you was a reminder of what this council stands for—community, leadership, and joy.

We’re just getting started, and there’s more in store for you in the coming days. So stay tuned, keep that smile on, and let’s continue creating the heartbeat of the ITHM community.

Photos by: Ashley Sunggayan, Enzo Abello

message.text:
𝐘𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐬 𝐌𝐚𝐝𝐞 𝐈𝐭 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐥-𝐍𝐨𝐰 𝐋𝐞𝐭’𝐬 𝐊𝐞𝐞𝐩 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐌𝐚𝐠𝐢𝐜 𝐆𝐨𝐢𝐧𝐠!

Thank you, ITHM Tams, for stopping by, sharing your smiles, and becoming part of our story at the ITHM Student Council booth! 

Every photo, every laugh, every moment spent with you was a reminder of what this council stands for—community, leadership, and joy.

We’re just getting started, and there’s more in store for you in the coming days. So stay tuned, keep that smile on, and let’s continue creating the heartbeat of the ITHM community.

Photos by: Ashley Sunggayan, Enzo Abello

#BidaSmileSaITHM
#TamHunt2025
#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil

message.text:
#IABFAdvisory
 
Re: E-Book Access for First Semester S.Y. 2025-2026

Attention, IABF!

For those utilizing E-Books as part of your course requirements, please take note of the following important reminders:
 
This semester, Digital Solutions (DS) access codes are obtained by signing the Student Undertaking form, with fees charged directly to your student account.

The corresponding amount appears in the Statement of Account within 1–2 months after receiving the access codes (Cengage and Pearson) or after account activation (McGraw-Hill).

Access codes are released daily, subject to stock availability. Requests submitted after 6:00 PM are processed the next business day.
 
Kindly scan the QR code or check the following links below:
 
CENGAGE
⁦https://bit.ly/CengageSU⁩
 
PEARSON
⁦https://bit.ly/PearsonSU⁩
 
MCGRAW-HILL
https://bit.ly/McgrawhillSU⁩  
 
Thank you for your cooperation.
 
Souce: Business Administration Department
 
#SoaringGreaterHeights
 
Pubmat by Yesha Eugenio and Alyanna Madrideo

#IABFAdvisory
 
Re: E-Book Access for First Semester S.Y. 2025-2026

Attention, IABF!

For those utilizing E-Books as part of your course requirements, please take note of the following important reminders:
 
This semester, Digital Solutions (DS) access codes are obtained by signing the Student Undertaking form, with fees charged directly to your student account.

The corresponding amount appears in the Statement of Account within 1–2 months after receiving the access codes (Cengage and Pearson) or after account activation (McGraw-Hill).

Access codes are released daily, subject to stock availability. Requests submitted after 6:00 PM are processed the next business day.
 
Kindly scan the QR code or check the following links below:
 
CENGAGE
⁦https://bit.ly/CengageSU⁩
 
PEARSON
⁦https://bit.ly/PearsonSU⁩
 
MCGRAW-HILL
https://bit.ly/McgrawhillSU⁩  
 
Thank you for your cooperation.
 
Souce: Business Administration Department
 
#SoaringGreaterHeights
 
Pubmat by Yesha Eugenio and Alyanna Madrideo

message.text:
#IABFAdvisory
 
Re: E-Book Access for First Semester S.Y. 2025-2026

Attention, IABF!

For those utilizing E-Books as part of your course requirements, please take note of the following important reminders:
 
This semester, Digital Solutions (DS) access codes are obtained by signing the Student Undertaking form, with fees charged directly to your student account.

The corresponding amount appears in the Statement of Account within 1–2 months after receiving the access codes (Cengage and Pearson) or after account activation (McGraw-Hill).

Access codes are released daily, subject to stock availability. Requests submitted after 6:00 PM are processed the next business day.
 
Kindly scan the QR code or check the following links below:
 
CENGAGE
⁦https://bit.ly/CengageSU⁩
 
PEARSON
⁦https://bit.ly/PearsonSU⁩
 
MCGRAW-HILL
https://bit.ly/McgrawhillSU⁩  
 
Thank you for your cooperation.
 
Souce: Business Administration Department
 
#SoaringGreaterHeights
 
Pubmat by Yesha Eugenio and Alyanna Madrideo
